  <title>Graphing Parabolas</title>

<commentary audience="instructor"><title>Overview</title>
<p>In this Lesson we consider the effects of the parameters <m>a</m>, <m>b</m>, and <m>c</m> on the graph of the basic parabola.  You could have students work on the Activities in groups, stopping to summarize after each part.</p></commentary>

