                  <commentary audience="instructor"><title>Note</title>
                  <p>Show the class how to find the <m>x</m>-coordinate of the vertex as the average of the -intercepts.  They will also need to be prompted on how to find the <m>y</m>-coordinate of the vertex.</p></commentary> 
                     
